!**/src/test/**/out/

## Eclipse
.project
.classpath
.settings/
bin/
!**/src/main/**/bin/
!**/src/test/**/bin/

## VS Code
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

## NetBeans
nbproject/private/
nbbuild/
dist/
nbdist/

